Package: PCA3Dviewer
Title: Interactive 3D PCA Viewer for 'genind' Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("James", "Hereward",
           email = "j.hereward@uq.edu.au",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Runs a principal component analysis on a 'genind' object (from the
    'adegenet' package) and writes a single, self-contained HTML file with an
    interactive 3D scatter plot rendered with three.js. The viewer supports
    selectable principal-component axes, a clickable population legend filter, a
    sample search box that highlights the matched sample with an arrow and
    label, a dark/light mode toggle, adjustable point size and opacity,
    switchable colour palettes, and PNG/PDF export.
